This product depends on third-party services and SDKs:

  - Anthropic SDK (Apache 2.0)
      https://github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-python
      Used for Claude API calls (personas + SME synthesis).

  - Voyage AI Python SDK (MIT)
      https://github.com/voyage-ai/voyageai-python
      Used for corpus embedding (voyage-3 model).

  - Qdrant Client (Apache 2.0)
      https://github.com/qdrant/qdrant-client
      Used for vector storage and retrieval.

  - Modal Python SDK (Apache 2.0)
      https://github.com/modal-labs/modal-client
      Used for serverless backend deployment.

The methodological framing (3-persona ensemble, Playing-to-Win
